---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-stone-900 text-stone-400 py-16 border-t border-stone-800 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background element -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-700 via-stone-700 to-amber-700 opacity-50"></div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <div class="reveal max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <p class="font-serif italic text-xl mb-6 text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">"El que lee mucho y anda mucho, ve mucho y sabe mucho."</p>
            
            <div class="flex justify-center items-center space-x-4 mb-8">
                <div class="h-px w-12 bg-stone-700"></div>
                <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-600 font-semibold">Miguel de Cervantes</span>
                <div class="h-px w-12 bg-stone-700"></div>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-sm mb-8 text-stone-500">
                &copy; {year} Jaime González Herráiz. Código licenciado bajo GNU GPLv3, contenido bajo Creative Commons BY-NC-SA 4.0.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm mb-8 text-stone-500">
                Esto es un trabajo de instituto. Te recomiendo ver cosas mejores que esta en mi web <a href="https://jaimegh.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-amber-700 hover:text-amber-500 underline underline-offset-2 decoration-stone-700 hover:decoration-amber-500 transition-all">jaimegh.com</a> y en la de mi marca <a href="https://inled.es" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-amber-700 hover:text-amber-500 underline underline-offset-2 decoration-stone-700 hover:decoration-amber-500 transition-all">Inled Group</a>.
            </p>
            <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-stone-800/50 border border-stone-800 text-xs text-stone-500 hover:text-stone-300 hover:border-stone-700 transition-colors">
                Fuente: <a href="https://elcorreoweb.es/sevilla/2022/08/04/ruta-azulejos-cervantinos-sevilla-105686985.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-amber-700 hover:text-amber-500 underline underline-offset-2 decoration-stone-700 hover:decoration-amber-500 transition-all">El Correo de Andalucía</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>